data.description: New construction without the wait! Immaculate home that is 3 year old. The home features four bedrooms and two bathrooms. The home also includes higher volume ceilings, an optional island, and LVP floors throughout the home. Kitchen includes stainless steel appliances. In the home, all bedrooms have closets, a full guest bathroom with extended vanity, and a dedicated laundry room. Kitchen overlooks the living and dining areas. Gramercy Farms gives you access to Lake Nona area within 20-25 minutes, FL turnpike in 10-15 minutes, All the Top area Attractions such as Disney World, Universal Studios, SeaWorld and world famous beaches are within 30-45min drive with MCO airport also within 30-45 minutes. St. Cloud area offers restaurants, shopping and much more without having to pay a premium.   SCHEDULE YOUR SHOWING TODAY!!!! TO MAKE THIS ONE OF KIND AS YOUR DREAM HOME.
